esm\u00f8ter i forbindelse med oppstart i barnehage og skole, men at n\u00e6rmilj\u00f8et er en viktig bidragsyter.", "- Det er veldig bra at de fikk god respons p\u00e5 Facebook. Det kan vi ta med oss, kanskje kan kommunen gj\u00f8re noe med det verkt\u00f8yet ogs\u00e5, sier han."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "a129ed446f4f5f457a6ac905c862515d7389e68690055775f6b1d17ae8edd212"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-07-05T12:54:47.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Alenepappa i L\u00f8kken fikk overveldende respons etter etterlysning."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/sortrondelag/article11271452.ece/71x2d4/ALTERNATES/w980-default/20150702_101110132.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/75219ab2fe56eefcd61c833138cb9bb7914cae5c.jpg?596d2084"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Fant nye lekekamerater til barna p\u00e5 Facebook -adressa.no", "Stor p\u00e5gang", "Ville bo p\u00e5 landet", "\u00c5pent og raust milj\u00f8"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "75219ab2fe56eefcd61c833138cb9bb7914cae5c"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Barnehage", "Skole", "S\u00f8r-Tr\u00f8ndelag"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Barnehage,Skole,S\u00f8r-Tr\u00f8ndelag"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "facebook"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["barna", "respons", "skole", "alenepappa"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["martine", "isabelle", "l\u00f8kken", "einum", "sofie"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["orkdal", "meldal", "bergen"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "cris robert 